Module slogo_team01

Package utilities.Commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddLineCommand
    Tells the BasicView object to add a line for the specific turtle index with given starting and ending coordinates.
    AddTurtleCommand
    This command object tells the basic view to add a new turtle with the given index.
    ClearScreenCommand
    This command object tells the front end view to clear it's screen.
    DisplayErrorCommand
    This command object tells the front end view to display an error message to the user.
    HideTurtleCommand
    This command object tells the front end view to hide a turtle.
    MoveTurtleCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to move a given turtle from one location to another.
    PenStatusCommand
    Command object that tells the front end whether the pen is up or down for a given turtle.
    RotateTurtleCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to rotate a turtle clockwise
    SetBackgroundColorCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to set the background of the turtle arena
    SetPaletteCommand
    Command object to update the palette with a new index and color values.
    SetPenColorCommand
    Command object that sets the pen color of a given turtle.
    SetPenSizeCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to change the pen size for a given turtle.
    SetShapeCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to change the shape of a given turtle.
    ShowTurtle
    Command object telling the front end to show a turtle on the screen.
    UpdateCommandHistoryCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to update its command history.
    UpdateCustomVariablesCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to update the user defined variables that have been entered by the user.
    UpdateUserCommandsCommand
    Command object that tells the front end to update its list of user defined commands entered thus far.
